        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Fair Pay for All Act of 20</b><strong>21</strong></p> <p>This bill expands the statutory protection against wage discrimination based on sex to include discrimination based on an employee's gender identity, sexual orientation, sex characteristics, a sex stereotype, pregnancy, childbirth, or a related medical condition. It also revises the protection to incorporate nonbinary gender identities.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
